          <span class="govuk-caption-m">Like Ghost Busters ... except for CS Acronyms!</span>
        </h1>

        <p>The Civil Service as an organisation, runs on Acronyms. Anyone
  new to a Department or area of work might think that their colleagues
  are speaking a different language.</p>
        <p>This site attempts to document all the acronyms used in order to improve everyoneâ€™s understanding in the workplace.</p>

